gps_trajectory.gps_map_generator module

gps_trajectory.gps_map_generator.generate_gps_map_from_excel(excel_path: str, output_html_path: str)[source]

Generates a GPS trajectory map from an Excel file and saves it as an HTML file.

Parameters:

  • excel_path (str) – Path to the Excel file containing ‘_time’, ‘Latitude’, and ‘Longitude’.

  • output_html_path (str) – Path where the HTML file with the map will be saved.
